FBIS4-60231 "drnes099_j_94001" FBIS-NES-94-099 Daily Report 20 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Southern Yemen To Announce Secession From North Southern Yemen To Announce Secession From North Announcement Expected `Soon' JN2005192194 Paris Radio Monte Carlo in Arabic 1900 GMT 20 May 94 JN2005192194 Paris Radio Monte Carlo Arabic BFN [Text] Reliable sources in Aden have said that the Yemeni Socialist Party [YSP] led by 'Ali Salim al-Bid will announce the establishment of the southern Yemeni state. The sources added that the decision has been made and that the official announcement on the establishment of the state will be made soon.
